{"tid":1624722,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【唔係廣告】元氣x榴槤壽司！！Starbucks咖啡x瑞典魔性臭魚！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:09:49.000Z","uid":86942,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1a53d47c7b80c3680c1c73993e8bf6456d5917","tid":1624722,"uid":86942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"放題食過一次榴槤炸彈，香味驚為天人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果陣香味<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">芳香四溢</span></span>、一傳千里，由內到外再到番內咁連珠爆發，啲<span style=\"color: gold;\">香味吸曬入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地毯[/size=4]</span>一留就留幾個星期，入埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">冷氣槽</span></span>就真係洗幾多次都唔掂！唔知既人路過真係以為去左<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榴槤樂園</span></span>！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvWjVfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvWjVfU.jpg&h=08a5664f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是，一向好鍾意食壽司既我，諗到神仙都羡慕既美味佳餚──<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榴槤壽司</span></span>，好可惜明將壽司已經創新不再，而且大家似乎都對<span style=\"color: orange;\">元氣情有獨鍾</span>。所以我諗過，雖然我地唔可以帶榴槤呢啲外來食物入去，但如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">自備榴槤醬料/漿/碎</span></span>入去添加風味又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5OVtzs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5OVtzs.png&h=9e1c28f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通既壽司上面<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">輕輕一抹</span></span>就可以變成榴槤壽司，再加上元氣呢個<span style=\"color: orange;\">火車直送gimmick</span>，只需要將榴槤漿放係<span style=\"color: violet;\">車軌上空</span>，火車就會<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高速滑過</span></span>並沾上醬料<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">昇格為榴槤壽司</span></span>！！聽落係咪非常吸引呢？唔知大家對呢個食法有冇興趣？記得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千奇唔好落錯係人地既壽司上面呀</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n雖然最近元氣好受歡迎，但即使冇位坐都可以係店<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">門口排隊</span></span>既時候食榴槤<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過下口癮</span></span>先！如果真係等唔切既，都可以買外賣<span style=\"color: orange;\">即場加上榴槤風味</span>，順便<span style=\"color: violet;\">派比周圍挨餓排隊既客人</span>推廣下創新食法，試過聞過既客人可能會<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂愛上</span></span>榴槤壽司<span style=\"color: red;\">搞到連元氣都冇興趣食添</span>！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>簡單</strong></span></span>得黎又咁有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">創意</span></strong></span>既食法，大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔會唔去幫手推廣下掛</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n______________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBHxHQnuJsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUBHxHQnuJsA&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d84929eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBHxHQnuJsA</a><br />\n而至於另一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">創新食法</span></span>，係一個好鍾意飲咖啡又好鍾意<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瑞典鹽醃鯡魚罐頭</span></span>既人諗出黎既，睇過條片就知道呢個聞名全球既罐頭係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">重口味過榴槤幾多倍</span></span>。聽人講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一邊飲咖啡一邊嘆鹽醃鯡魚</span></span>味道簡直天作之合！可惜我唔知邊度有得買，如果搵到既我都想搵日<span style=\"color: red;\">一邊嘆Starbucks既極品咖啡配上呢個鹽醃鯡魚做小食</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過要注意番，個罐頭<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好圓好易跌</span></span>，千奇<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千奇唔好倒瀉</span></span>左係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地毯</span></span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梳化</span></span>等等<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">難以清潔既地方</span></span>，唔係就會好頭痕架啦！！<br />\n<br />\n______________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n除左呢兩個<del>美心</del>、呀唔係、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">美食組合</span></span>之外，大J都推介左唔少<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">等待大家發掘</span></span>既美食組合，如果大家諗到既一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">po上黎分享</span></span>下呀！<br />\n美食channel : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/JStud1o/search?query=%E8%87%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FJStud1o%2Fsearch%3Fquery%3D%25E8%2587%25AD&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=cf1b4bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/JStud1o/search?query=%E8%87%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">廣傳分享</span></span>，比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔同年齡</span></span>、[size=5]<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔同承擔能力</span></span>既人都可以開開心心加入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>美食家</ins></strong></span></span>行列，除左日日撳飛之外都可以<span style=\"color: violet;\">大飽口福</span>～～"},{"pid":"b46c7bbf7e9dfa332ccac1c074463c595b754c4d","tid":1624722,"uid":86942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2211e55ed051c11eb92ec45882e5083ec4cf4604","tid":1624722,"uid":247896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj